! STEOM-CCSD STO-3G TightSCF
# High print level to dump dressed STEOM intermediates / full CI eigenvectors,
# so the Python g_phph can be diffed element-wise with NO reconstruction noise.
%mdci
  nroots 8
  DoSTEOM true
  DoTriplet true
  DoCISNat false
  NActIP 6
  NActEA 4
  PrintLevel 4
end
%output
  PrintLevel 4
end
* xyz 0 1
O    0.000000000000     0.000000000000     0.683000000000
C    0.000000000000     0.000000000000    -0.534000000000
H    0.000000000000     0.926000000000    -1.129000000000
H    0.000000000000    -0.926000000000    -1.129000000000
*
